#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "--renderer={renderer}"
msgstr "--renderer={renderer}"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify which graphical renderer to use. On all platforms, “opengl” and "
"software are available. On Windows, you can use “direct3d11” or “direct3d12” "
"(if it was compiled with Qt ≥ 6.6). On &macOS;, you can use “metal”."
msgstr ""
"指定使用的图形渲染器。在所有平台上，都可使用“opengl” 和“software”。在 "
"Windows 上，你可以使用“direct3d11”或“direct3d12” (若使用 Qt >= 6.6 进行编"
"译) 。在&macOS;上，你可以使用“metal”。 "

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid "--software-renderer"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use software renderer instead of OpenGL (should work with any graphical "
"card). Deprecated, use “--renderer=software” instead."
msgstr ""
"使用软件渲染器而非 openGL  (理论上适用于任何显卡) 。已弃用，请改用 --"
"renderer=software 。 "

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid "--opengl-renderer"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use OpenGL renderer instead of software (faster and more graphical effects "
"but can crash with some graphical cards). Deprecated, use “--"
"renderer=opengl” instead."
msgstr ""
"使用 openGL 渲染器而非软件渲染器 (速度更快且图形效果更佳，但在某些显卡上可能"
"崩溃) 。已弃用，请改用 \"--renderer=opengl\"。"

